# Project-level Maven CLI options. Picked up automatically by Maven from
# ${project.basedir}/.mvn/maven.config; one option per line.
#
# Silence two harmless WARNs emitted by the networknt JSON-schema validator
# embedded in cyclonedx-core-java (used by cyclonedx-maven-plugin). They are
# triggered by CycloneDX-specific schema annotations the validator doesn't
# recognize ("meta:enum", "deprecated") and have no impact on BOM correctness:
#   [WARNING] Unknown keyword meta:enum  - you should define your own Meta Schema...
#   [WARNING] Unknown keyword deprecated - you should define your own Meta Schema...
-Dorg.slf4j.simpleLogger.log.com.networknt.schema=error

